    "In the myeloid compartment, we observed a decrease of Kupffer cell proportions in post-PVE tissues, accompanied by an increase in other Monocyte/Macrophage populations (Fig. 5d), such as those expressing IGSF21, a gene with a proinflammatory role 32; and TREM2+ Monocytes, which have previously been identified as a scar-associated macrophage subtype.",
